Interface Summary

GetCommentsRunnableInterface Provides an interface for a Runnable that gets Comments from ElasticSearch.
GetImageRunnableInterface Provides an interface for a Runnable that gets an image from ElasticSearch.
GetPOIRunnableInterface Provides an interface for a Runnable that gets a point of interest from ElasticSearch.
GetThreadCommentsRunnableInterface Provides an interface for a Runnable that gets ThreadComments from ElasticSearch.

PostRunnableInterface Provides an interface for a Runnable that posts a ThreadComment or Comment to ElasticSearch.
TaskInterface Provides an interface for a Task that runs one or several runnables, for use with the ThreadManager for asynchronous tasks.
UpdateDialogListenerInterface Provides an interface for a DialogListener that performs some action on receiving some message.
UpdateRunnableInterface Provides an interface for a Runnable that updates a list of Comments on ElasticSearch.
